---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "May 23, 2026";
---

<Layout title="Now | Kundai Chatambudza">
  <div class="space-y-10">
    <section>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Now</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300">What I'm currently doing, reading, listening to, and watching.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#1e242a] rounded-lg p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Currently</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
        <p>
          I'm currently working across mobile apps, AI-assisted development, and early-stage product building.
        </p>
        <p>
          At <strong>MOHARA</strong>, I work on React Native and full-stack TypeScript projects, with recent experience across technical solution design, backend integrations, CI/CD, and production mobile app delivery.
        </p>
        <p>
          Recently, I helped build <strong>Mindfull</strong>, a custom iOS and Android health and wellness app that replaced a previous white-label product. Before that, I led frontend architecture for <strong>Louvelle</strong>, a high-fashion peer-to-peer rental iOS app, and worked on projects like the <strong>Taos Ski Valley</strong> website and <strong>Uply</strong> recruitment platform.
        </p>
        <p>
          Outside of MOHARA, I'm a co-founder of <strong>AgriData Technologies</strong>. We're building agricultural intelligence tools for institutions in Zimbabwe, combining WhatsApp-based pest and disease reporting with real-time dashboards, maps, severity tracking, and alerts.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm also working as a builder on a <strong>BOQ Generator</strong> app, helping turn project requirements into structured bills of quantities and reducing manual admin work for teams.
        </p>
        <p>
          My current learning focus is React Native architecture, full-stack TypeScript, database design, AI-assisted development, technical leadership, and product strategy.
        </p>
        <p>
          On the side, I'm exploring <strong>Voessa</strong>, an AI voice coaching app, and <strong>Quest</strong>, a gamified personal growth app.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not coding, I'm usually learning guitar, writing notes, thinking about mindfulness and ethics, or exploring product ideas.
        </p>
        <p class="pt-2">
          This page was inspired by the <a href="https://nownownow.com" class="text-orange-500 hover:underline">now page movement</a> — regularly updated to reflect what I'm focused on at this point in my life.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>